@startuml C1_Manage_Docks_Process_View
title C1 – Manage Docks (Process View)

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "DocksController\n(API Layer)" as Controller
participant "DockMapper\n(Data Mapper)" as Mapper
participant "PortContext\n(EF Core)" as Context
database "Database\n(SQL / InMemory)" as DB

Officer -> Controller : POST /api/Docks\n(CreateDockDTO)
Controller -> Mapper : Converte DTO → Entidade de Domínio
Mapper --> Controller : Retorna objeto Dock

Controller -> Context : Adiciona entidade Dock
Context -> DB : Persiste dados (SaveChanges)
DB --> Context : Confirma inserção
Context --> Controller : OK

Controller --> Officer : HTTP 201 Created\n(DockDTO)

@enduml

